{"tid":2372682,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過返工屙屎屙屙下瞓著咗？","createTime":"2021-01-20T01:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T06:11:01.000Z","uid":40930,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31c24a839820d9e17fbd0db8a14605fddade5a9c","tid":2372682,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:24:06.000Z","msg":"返工每日屙屎都預咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日入去屎塔除咗屙屎都會做大大小小唔同嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但你又有冇試過屙屙下瞓著咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇就應該要試下，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒咗我會當自己重新做人咁，當自己新嚟屙屎，重新計時<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果就好似賺咗兩倍積分咁開心，又坐過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出返嚟office 又係一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab0e22a417d307c57ae21a1d2b2cb6af8642374","tid":2372682,"uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:25:56.000Z","msg":"試過訓訓吓痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8581f32826fac6eb0138dbdc2d0bd52b3fe03984","tid":2372682,"uid":148056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:48:13.000Z","msg":"未抆屎就訓屎眼啲屎咪乾撚晒？"},{"pid":"5fd78a265d301e442a575cafe77d8377e314725c","tid":2372682,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"有無人拎報紙入廁所睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc67e5b2b842fdae1d678b7c86a4cc7002a403c8","tid":2372682,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ab0e22a417d307c57ae21a1d2b2cb6af8642374","tid":2372682,"uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:25:56.000Z","msg":"試過訓訓吓痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wai